    <section id="live-sound" class="bg-grey">
        <h2 class="section-title">Live Sound</h2>
        <div class="about-text">
            At <span class="highlight">ZoVaa Music Productions</span>,
            live sound is more than amplification — it is
            <span class="highlight">clarity</span>,
            <span class="highlight">control</span>, and
            <span class="highlight">consistency</span> in every environment.
            <br><br>

            Our system is built around
            <span class="highlight">PS Audio speaker systems</span>, delivering
            <span class="highlight">wide dispersion</span>,
            <span class="highlight">tight low-end response</span>, and
            <span class="highlight">detailed high-frequency clarity</span>
            across the entire venue.
            <br><br>

            Powered by
            <span class="highlight">Chevin high-linearity amplifiers</span>,
            we ensure exceptional <span class="highlight">headroom</span>,
            <span class="highlight">dynamic accuracy</span>, and reliable performance
            even under demanding live conditions.
            <br><br>

            At the heart of our control sits the
            <span class="highlight">Allen & Heath digital mixing console</span>,
            providing <span class="highlight">precise signal processing</span>,
            <span class="highlight">flexible routing</span>, and
            <span class="highlight">surgical mix control</span>.
            <br><br>

            For capture, we rely on industry-trusted microphones from
            <span class="highlight">Shure</span>,
            <span class="highlight">AKG</span>,
            <span class="highlight">Sennheiser</span>, and
            <span class="highlight">Audix</span> —
            ensuring every vocal and instrument is reproduced with
            <span class="highlight">definition</span>,
            <span class="highlight">presence</span>, and
            <span class="highlight">natural character</span>.
            <br><br>

            The result is a <span class="highlight">coherent signal chain</span>
            designed to translate the artist’s performance with
            <span class="highlight">power</span>,
            <span class="highlight">transparency</span>, and
            <span class="highlight">professional impact</span> —
            from stage to audience.
        </div>
